Senator representing Bayelsa East Senatorial District at the National Assembly Senator Biobarakuma Degi-Eremienyo, Minister of State Petroleum Resources Chief Timipre Sylva, Chairman Bayelsa State All Progressives Congress (APC) Dr Denis Otiotio and leader of The Good People of Nigeria group, after the procurement and presentation of APC presidential nomination form to him, at the NNPC Towers, Abuja, on Monday